{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_akafyu_set_1", "eventName": "異鄉劍士", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "異鄉劍士", "storyInfo": "被驅逐的劍士漂泊至他鄉，她在這裡度過了平凡的一天。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_indoor_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大人，這次作戰失利責任全在我指揮失當，未能識破敵人奸計，所有罪責由屬下一人承擔！"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "屬下深知自己罪不容誅，我一人死不足惜，但屬下只求一個最後報答大人的機會，我定能——"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "定能如何？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "若我今日判你身死，或是讓你死於戰場，是能挽回戰敗對局勢的影響，還是能讓那些因你而死的戰士復生？你又如何擔得起責？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你究竟，將戰爭當作何物？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大人！我——"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "赤冬，你沒有資格留在這裡。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "離開東國。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$sjoyasorrow_intro", "key": "$sjoyasorrow_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spear", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_singleblunt"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spear", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "九百九十八......九百九十九......一千......", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劍士收起長劍，深深吐納。抽出隨身小刀在牆上的計數符號上又刻下一劃。"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被驅逐出東國的第一百三十七天，停留在這座名為龍門的陌生城市的第三十九天。"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離開東國之前，收到了一家名為“羅德島”的公司的邀請，他們說自己依然有可以作為劍士而戰的機會——大抵也是主上的默許。"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今自己要做的就是在這裡耐心等待，等待對方接頭人帶自己去新的安身地點——某個遠離東國的地方。"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前路未卜。"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鍛煉從未懈怠，可刀油已經用完了。", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如何是好......", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們常說，落單的劍士脆弱如羽獸。曾經握在手中的劍越是鋒銳，便越是易折。"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離開東國前遇到過數次幾乎致命的麻煩，之後的路雖相對安穩，可也不清楚是否還有敵人跟隨自己來到此處，萬萬不能掉以輕心。"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照約定，每十天會有人按時將必需的生活物資留在門口，自己不該隨意離開這間屋子。"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_open_box", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wind", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天似乎也沒有異樣......", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暫住的居所地處城市週邊的一條老舊小巷中，絲毫不引人注目，應該還算安全。"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "偶有形形色色的路人路過，還有每日都會按時擺攤的早餐店主，沒有發現可疑的人。"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從窗戶可以看到這座陌生城市一隅。龍門的模樣和家鄉大不相同，與傳聞中南朝治下的光怪陸離的城市倒有幾分相似。"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "食物都已經消耗盡了，今天本該是補充物資的時間。", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知周圍是否還有追兵潛藏，貿然出行恐怕還是有危險......", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖......何等令人煩躁，堂堂劍士豈有避戰畏敵的道理！光嚴家的劍士何曾有過這般屈辱！", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "適應環境，是必要的修行......", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hungry", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按時進食也是......", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_lungmen_b", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深巷。"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劍士謹慎地踏出一步，月餘來第一次走出房間，第一次從低處觀察這片空間。"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小巷兩側低矮的房屋緊緊擠挨著，露出狹窄的一方天空，劍士恍惚想起神社低矮的屋簷。"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看上去是老舊的民居，並無特殊之處。建築上懸掛的雜物眾多，也無合適的狙擊位。", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "進出都只有一個口，就算有跟蹤者，應該很難隱藏蹤跡。可若遇到伏兵堵截，敵眾我寡時，脫身同樣麻煩。", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "此地不宜久——", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_firemagic", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_sp_ballista", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n", "volume": 0.5, "delay": 1.5}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隊長！小心弩炮！", "name": "驚慌的聲音"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們已經中了埋伏，敵人數量太多，繼續苦戰也是不會有結果的......", "name": "驚慌的聲音"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "振作起來，我們一起殺出去！", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n", "volume": 0.5, "delay": 1.5}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請您先撤退吧！我們會為您斷後的！", "name": "驚慌的聲音"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再睜開眼，身旁空無一人。"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_smithy", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陽光燦爛，和那個雪天所見的陽光別無二致，湧入鼻腔的卻是臨街店鋪傳來的油煙味。"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_032", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老闆，今天怎麼大清早就開始做炒菜啊？", "name": "路過的食客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_005"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "偶爾試試換個花樣，最近年輕人起床越來越晚，早午飯都合一頓了，我也得跟著適應不是？", "name": "早餐店老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_005"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冷靜些......不能因為過去的失敗失態......冷靜些。", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_005"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位姑娘，還沒吃飯吧，吃點什麼東西？", "name": "早餐店老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_005"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再怎麼匆忙，還是要好好吃飯啊。", "name": "早餐店老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_005"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（常見的街邊飯店。店主人和客人都是普通人，感受不到危險的氣息。）", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（或許可以用這裡的食物充饑。）", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡，都提供什麼食物？", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_005"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "豆漿油條，包子炒麵，什麼都有。這裡的客人都說我們家的腸粉是一絕，您要不要嚐嚐？", "name": "早餐店老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_005"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（面皮包裹著看不清的餡料，還有來路不明的醬汁，這香味的確是容易讓人精神動搖......）", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（不......不妥，還是得尋找更為安全的食物才行。）", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "300,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_032"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛才那個人怎麼回事，看上去像是沒有帶錢？", "name": "路過的食客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_005"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有些面生，好像不是住這附近的人吧。", "name": "早餐店老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_005"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那姑娘看上去面黃肌瘦的，怕是有陣子都沒好好吃飯了。唉，要是口袋裡緊張的話，請她一頓也不要緊的呀。", "name": "早餐店老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_005"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_lungmen_m", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_horn", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "碼頭。"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城市的重要出入口，人流量最為龐大的地方之一。如果與自己接頭的人來自更遠的地方，他有可能會出現在這裡。"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劍士站在高處凝神眺望，稍遠處，大型艦船吞吐著數量龐大的貨物和人群，稍作停頓又匆忙駛向遠方。"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其中是不是也有一條船，可以直接駛向東國......"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不......還遠不是回去的時候。", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以敗軍之將的身份被驅逐，之後便再無作為，就算回到故土，又有何面目去見大人......", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_272_strong_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老闆......打擾一下......您踩到我的貨箱了......", "name": "水產小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_272_strong_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？抱歉......", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_272_strong_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老闆，要買鱗嗎？", "name": "水產小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_272_strong_1#2$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新鮮的鱗，種類挺全的，都是今天剛送來的。可以幫您切好，也可以現做成刺身。", "name": "水產小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_272_strong_1#2$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（刺身......熟悉的食物。）", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（沒有多餘的烹飪手法，不用加多餘的調味料，是安全的食物。）", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要。一條鱗，做成刺身。", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_272_strong_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好嘞，一份刺身，您稍等。", "name": "水產小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_272_strong_1#4$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 7.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 40.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "false", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$gavel1", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$gavel1", "volume": 0.5, "delay": 0.2, "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$gavel1", "volume": 0.5, "delay": 0.4, "channel": "b"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（這個小販，竟然有如此身手？）", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（將一把普通的剔骨刀運用得如此精妙。手臂肌肉發力的方式，刀鋒入肉的角度，皆合乎劍理。）", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如此精湛的刀法......", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......叫什麼名字？", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "刀法是何人所授，流派可有名號，這把刀可有來歷？", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_272_strong_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老闆......您問我嗎？", "name": "水產小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_272_strong_1#2$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我叫孑，是個水產販子，用刀的本事是我阿伯教給我的......", "name": "水產小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_272_strong_1#2$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這把刀就是用來切鱗的，沒切過別的東西。您問流派......處理殼蝦和鱗確實是要用不同的刀具和手法......", "name": "水產小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_272_strong_1#2$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來是閉關修煉的流派，定力可敬......", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在神社裡也見過十年如一日只劈砍草席修煉的劍客。將一個普通的招式修煉到出神入化，同樣有驚人威力。", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有這樣的身手，卻淪落至鱗肆肉鋪之間......看來你也是不得志的劍士。在這一點上，我們也算是同病相憐了。", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我且問你，將來可有什麼志向？準備用這身武藝為誰效力？", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_272_strong_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我沒什麼大志向......", "name": "水產小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_272_strong_1#2$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼前的理想就是生意能好一點，多存一點錢，儘早換一家更大的鋪面......", "name": "水產小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_272_strong_1#2$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是什麼話，這樣的刀法只用來砍切這些小玩意，你就不覺得可惜？", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_272_strong_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小玩意？老闆是嫌這條鱗小嗎？）", "name": "水產小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_272_strong_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個......大一點的鱗當然也有，都是按斤數賣，不貪您便宜。我就是怕您吃不完......", "name": "水產小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_272_strong_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（話裡有話，反而借飯量拷問我嗎？）", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開什麼玩笑，“有多大的飯量就有多大能耐”，區區一條鱗，哪有吃不完的道理！儘管挑你這最大的鱗端上來！", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_272_strong_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好......好！", "name": "水產小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_272_strong_1#4$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來取預訂貨物。", "name": "冷酷的聲音"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "草鱗，一條，殼蝦，三斤。", "name": "冷酷的聲音"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_272_strong_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，都備好了。給，您拿好。", "name": "水產小販"}, "figure_art": "avg_272_strong_1#2$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_118_yuki", "posfrom": "-150,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰？！", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人群中，一個熟悉的身影飄然掠過。腳步很輕，動作很快。就像偶然躍出水面的鱗，轉眼間又遁入江中，無跡可尋。"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那樣的裝扮......南朝的忍者？為什麼會出現在這裡？！", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "站住！", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing4", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing5", "volume": 0.9, "delay": 0.15, "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大人！屬下護駕來遲，您還安好嗎？！", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒事。", "name": "穩重的聲音"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些忍者，三番五次意圖暗殺，實在卑鄙！他們自知無法在戰場上光明正大地戰勝您，就只會使這些下三濫的手段！", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赤冬，你可知道，這些人為什麼想要殺我？", "name": "穩重的聲音"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，您是光嚴家的重臣，最驍勇的戰將。他們忌憚您，才會想對您不利。", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，這是派他們前來殺我的人的理由，而並非是他們的。", "name": "穩重的聲音"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可悲的是，恐怕這些倒在地上的人，他們至死都不知道。", "name": "穩重的聲音"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赤冬，你不該和他們一樣。"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_lmstreet_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長街。"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跋涉許久，時間已經入夜。"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "街上張燈結彩，眼前盡是望不到頭的霓虹燈牌和高樓大廈，耳邊路人歡聲笑語不斷——今天難道是這異邦的某個節日嗎？"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人潮洶湧，劍士佇立其中，像是被浪潮反覆拍打的礁石。而追蹤的目標早已不見了身影。"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早有預謀嗎？故意引我來這種地方......", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鬧市殺人，那些卑鄙忍者最慣用的伎倆......這裡是他們的主場。", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巷戰並非我所長，可若喪失戰意，只會讓他們更輕易得手。", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到底在哪......！", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劍士緊緊握住刀柄，屏氣凝神，想要從喧囂聲中分辨出那一絲危險的響動，可總是徒勞。"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 15.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_swordexsheath"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼人——！", "name": "赤冬"}, "figure_art": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_033"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老兄！你這身裝備好酷！簡直和真的一樣！", "name": "興奮的青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_033"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赤冬回過頭，一個年輕人正觸摸著自己的肩甲，眼裡閃著興奮的光芒。"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劍士正要發作，可眼前的年輕人無知的神情讓她奇怪又陌生——哪有平民敢這樣堂而皇之地靠近全副武裝的武士？"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_033", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不怕我？", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_033", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怕？為什麼？", "name": "興奮的青年"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天不是《南北風雲傳》發售預告的第一天嗎？你是怎麼提前弄到這身衣服的設計圖的？我懂了，你是官方請來做宣傳的模特兒吧？", "name": "興奮的青年"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這身鎧甲是北朝光嚴派的劍士對不對！聽說北朝劍士基礎屬性很強，南朝的忍者操作上限高。但我覺得還是劍士的裝備更帥一點！", "name": "興奮的青年"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在胡說些什麼......", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "忍者？你剛才有見到一個忍者嗎？", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_033", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喏，看那邊。", "name": "興奮的青年"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赤冬順著年輕人手指的方向看去，炫彩的燈光讓赤冬眼花繚亂，她費了些功夫才將視線聚焦在路旁電玩店的大螢幕上。"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遊戲裡角色裝備著與自己幾乎一模一樣的鎧甲和長刀，使出自己萬萬做不到的招式動作，在數量誇張的敵軍中大殺四方。"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "螢幕裡的人血肉橫飛，痛哭哀號；螢幕外的人興高采烈，大呼小叫。"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "透亮的櫥窗照出自己的影子，像是個滑稽的異類。"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劍士突然笑出了聲。"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵......", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生活在這個地方，你很幸運。", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drawsword"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望你永遠都不用害怕這個東西......", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是記著，這個東西，一點也不酷。", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_lungmen_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_090", "posfrom": "150,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_090", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赤冬？", "name": "羅德島幹員"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個標誌......羅德島？", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_090", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來的路上不太順利，耽誤了一點時間。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉讓你久等了，這邊生活還算順心？沒有遇到麻煩吧？", "name": "羅德島幹員"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是個奇怪的地方，但也算有趣......", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，你是烏薩斯人？", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_090", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，為了避免麻煩我還專門做了打扮來著......是口音暴露了嗎？好吧沒錯，我確實是烏薩斯人。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與東國有聯絡，又雇傭了烏薩斯人......", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“羅德島”，到底是什麼地方？", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_090", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是個和平的地方。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那裡有烏薩斯人，也有東國人，還有卡西米爾人、萊塔尼亞人。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒不是說要讓所有人都假裝那些不愉快的事沒有發生一樣，只是在那裡，仇恨和暴力不會是我們辦事的邏輯。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可有人告訴我，在羅德島，我還是可以作為劍士而戰。", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_090", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。羅德島還有很多和你一樣的優秀的戰士——我們確實是醫療公司，可為了救人，還是有需要打架的時候的。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但更多時候，大家還是做著普通的事，吃吃飯喝喝茶，然後想辦法避免出現必須要打架的情況。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼......", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有意思。我願意去看看。", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_090", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，你比我想像的要好打交道多了。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有沒有要收拾的行李，我們可以出發了嗎？", "name": "羅德島幹員"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_475_akafyu_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拿著這把刀就夠了。走吧。", "name": "赤冬"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "主上，我會繼續學習的。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我會去學著理解戰鬥的意義，我會找到劍鋒應當指向的方向。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}